extends layout

block content
	section.hero
		.container
			span
				p Analytics4Athletes helps athletes, teams, trainers, coaches, agents, etc. take their game to the next level by improving how analytics and statistics are presented to them.
				a.button(href='#details') Learn More
			img(src="/images/analytics_examples.png" alt="Analytics Example")
	section.more-info
		.container#details
			img(src="/images/logo_simple.png" alt="Analytics 4 Athletes Logo")
			p At <span>Analytics4Athletes</span> we use statistics to help visualize the areas where coaches, trainers, and athletes are not only excelling but also where they could use the most work. This helps to determine the best course of action to move forward, highlights the key areas to focus on, and as a result helps to make the biggest improvements.
			.column
				h3 For Trainers and Coaches
				p <span>Analytics4Athletes</span> helps both trainers and coaches become more marketable by providing real time examples as to how much an athlete improves their game while training within their program/system.
			.column
				h3 For the Athlete
				p <span>Analytics4Athletes</span> also helps the athletes themselves, by providing a statistical breakdowns of a season, to help highlight the areas to work on, in order to make the biggest improvements to their game.
	section.products
		.container
			h2 Products
			.box.player-analysis
				!= h.icon('user')
				h4 Player Analysis
				p Player Analysis Sheets provide coaches, trainers, scouts etc. statistical insight as to where an athlete is really excelling and to areas where he/she can improve on. This is available to football, basketball, and baseball.
				a.button(href='/player-analysis') Learn More
			.box.player-development
				!= h.icon('user')
				h4 Player Development
				p Player Development Sheets are for trainers and coaches to visually show what they need to work on with an individual athlete with detailed analysis. This is only available for basketball players, from the high school to professional levels.
				a.button(href='/player-development') Learn More
			.box.team-scouting
				!= h.icon('group')
				h4 Team Scouting Report
				p Team Scouting Reports are for basketball coaches to receive in-depth statistical analysis for a team. These reports cover offensive and defensive plays and strategies, success rates, and things that need improvement.
				a.button(href='/team-scouting-report') Learn More